Tacheles - Audio samples license
=================================

This directory (app/audio/) contains synthesized Hebrew speech samples generated
with ElevenLabs (https://elevenlabs.io). The application CODE is covered by the
repository's main license; THESE AUDIO FILES are NOT, and are licensed separately
as follows.

License: Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial 4.0 International (CC BY-NC 4.0)
         https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc/4.0/
         PLUS the additional restriction below.

Attribution: "Voice generated with ElevenLabs (elevenlabs.io)."

Additional restriction (No AI/ML training):
  The audio files may NOT be used, in whole or in part, as input to, or as part of
  a dataset for, training, fine-tuning, developing, testing, or improving any
  machine-learning or artificial-intelligence model or system.

Why these terms: the samples are output of the ElevenLabs service. Under the
ElevenLabs Prohibited Use Policy, output may not be made available to others on
terms less restrictive or more permissive than those under which it was obtained
(section 9(n)), and may not be used to train AI/ML models (sections 9(k)/(l)).
Non-commercial + attribution + no-AI-training mirrors those obligations so that
redistributing the files here stays within ElevenLabs' terms.

This is a good-faith lay reading of the ElevenLabs terms, not legal advice. Before
any public release, re-check the current ElevenLabs terms and, if in doubt, confirm
with ElevenLabs support.
